WEBVTT

00:00.161 --> 00:03.311
Previously on <i>The Secret Life</i>
<i>of the American Teenager...</i>

00:03.411 --> 00:05.679
I'm getting more uncomfortable
by the minute.

00:05.680 --> 00:07.247
What do you think might help?

00:07.248 --> 00:10.050
Maybe when we go see Dr. Attavi
today, he can suggest something.

00:10.051 --> 00:12.435
Does it bother you that Ben
and Adrian are now married?

00:12.436 --> 00:13.346
Why should it?

00:13.354 --> 00:15.689
Did you have sex?
I did.

00:15.690 --> 00:16.923
Maybe I'm not really
in love with her.

00:16.924 --> 00:18.925
Don't ever ask to borrow
the apartment again.

00:18.926 --> 00:22.529
Welcome Mr. and Mrs. Ben Boykewich
back to school.

00:22.530 --> 00:24.698
[cheering]
Thank you, everyone.

00:24.699 --> 00:26.199
I met George when we
were leaving the wedding.

00:26.200 --> 00:27.367
You can't go out with him.

00:27.368 --> 00:29.402
You let Madison and Jack
have sex in your bed?

00:29.403 --> 00:31.438
If you're ready to take this
relationship seriously, so am I.

00:31.439 --> 00:33.406
I don't want to be friends
with my old boyfriend.

00:33.407 --> 00:34.941
You're not friends
with your old girlfriend.

00:34.942 --> 00:36.142
I still hear from her
once in a while.

00:36.143 --> 00:38.044
What?
You should meet Angie.

00:38.045 --> 00:41.781
I really love you, but sex isn't right
for the two of us right now.

00:41.782 --> 00:43.116
When's your husband
getting back in town?

00:43.117 --> 00:45.652
He really loves it there
in-- in Zimbabwe.

00:45.653 --> 00:47.954
You think maybe the two of us
can drive up the coast

00:47.955 --> 00:49.456
and have dinner somewhere
on the beach?

00:49.457 --> 00:51.625
Maybe even spend the night
at a decent hotel.

00:51.626 --> 00:54.060
Something just--
just doesn't feel right.

00:54.061 --> 00:56.563
You don't think
that you're going into labor?

00:57.665 --> 01:00.367
I'm not sure.

